            <p class="text-white mb-5">Tu crédito ya está pre-autorizado</p>
            <a href="https://nueva.percapita.mx/sign-up/title" class="px-15 py-2 rounded-md text-[#005593] font-extrabold" style="background: linear-gradient(153deg,#00bfff 13%,#41e6ed 53%,#41e6ed)">Solicitar credito</a>
